    "ocr_text": "In addition to the foregoing, the attention of the members of the Executive Council is again called to the fact that a meeting will be held of the Executive Council beginning at 10 o'clock, Tuesday morning, June 15th, 1909, at the Victoria Hotel, upon 27th and Broadway, New York City. \n\nWith best wishes, I am \nFraternally yours,\n[signed] Samuel Gompers\nPresident,\nAmerican Federation of Labor.",
    "summary": "Notification of an Executive Council meeting for the American Federation of Labor to be held at 10 o'clock on Tuesday morning, June 15th, 1909, at the Victoria Hotel, New York City.",
